OL,3,CHit and run driver jailed after
OL,4,Cleaving victim bleeding in the road
OL,6,FA woman has been jailed after she
OL,7,Fcrashed into a teenage cyclist and
OL,8,Fabandoned him bleeding in the road.
OL,10,FA court heard Tanya Johnston could not
OL,11,Fsee out of her foggy windscreen when
OL,12,Fshe turned into a junction on the
OL,13,Fwrong side of the road and collided
OL,14,Fhead on with the then 17-year-old boy.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
