OL,3,CHit and run driver jailed after
OL,4,Cleaving victim bleeding in the road
OL,6,FPolice were called at 10.10pm on
OL,7,FMonday 20 February 2023 to reports of
OL,8,Fa hit and run collision at the
OL,9,Fjunction of Norn Hill and Lefroy
OL,10,FAvenue, Basingstoke. A young cyclist
OL,11,Fhad been hit by a blue Vauxhall Corsa
OL,12,Fand sustained serious head injuries,
OL,13,Fbut the vehicle involved in the
OL,14,Fcollision had left the scene.
OL,16,FPolice administered first aid until
OL,17,Fthe ambulance service arrived and took
OL,18,Fthe teenager to hospital. His injuries
OL,19,Fwere so severe he had to have facial
OL,20,Freconstruction surgery and will have
OL,21,Flife-long scarring to his face.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
