CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1783855166
OL,3,CHit and run driver jailed after
OL,4,Cleaving victim bleeding in the road
OL,6,FWitnesses saw the Corsa being driven
OL,7,Faway from the scene and officers
OL,8,Flocated it in nearby Bennet Close with
OL,9,Fconsiderable damage to the windscreen.
OL,11,FThe vehicle was registered and insured
OL,12,Fto Tanya Johnston but when police
OL,13,Fattended her home she wasn't there.
OL,15,FIt wasn't until two days after the
OL,16,Fcollision that 47 year-old Johnston
OL,17,Fhanded herself into Basingstoke Police
OL,18,Fstation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
