CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1783855166
OL,3,CHit and run driver jailed after
OL,4,Cleaving victim bleeding in the road
OL,6,FIn her interview she admitted her
OL,7,Fwindscreen was misted up and she did
OL,8,Fnot have a good view of the road.
OL,10,FShe was sentenced at Winchester Crown
OL,11,FCourt to 18 months imprisonment for
OL,12,Fcausing serious injury by careless
OL,13,Fdriving. She was also sentenced for
OL,14,Fdangerous driving after she fled the
OL,15,Fscene, continuing to drive with a
OL,16,Fsmashed windscreen. She had previously
OL,17,Fpled guilty to both charges.
OL,19,FUpon her release from custody, she
OL,20,Fwill also be banned from driving for a
OL,21,Ffurther two years.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
