FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1783855166
OL,3,CHit and run driver jailed after
OL,4,Cleaving victim bleeding in the road
OL,6,FPolice Sergeant James Hall said: "This
OL,7,Fdriver showed utter disregard for the
OL,8,Fsafety of others. By driving that car
OL,9,Fwhen she clearly could not see
OL,10,Fproperly, she put the lives of all
OL,11,Froad users in danger.
OL,13,F"To make matters worse she drove off,
OL,14,Fleaving the victim at the scene
OL,15,Fwithout making any calls for help,
OL,16,Fthen failed to own up to what had
OL,17,Fhappened for two days.
OL,26,@nD@bOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
