FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1783855166
OL,3,CHit and run driver jailed after
OL,4,Cleaving victim bleeding in the road
OL,6,F"This person's careless actions have
OL,7,Fnow changed the life of a young man as
OL,8,Fhe has injuries he will live with
OL,9,Fforever. Despite this he has shown
OL,10,Fmaturity beyond his years at every
OL,11,Fstage of our investigation, and I want
OL,12,Fto thank him for everything he has
OL,13,Fdone to help us bring this woman to
OL,14,Fjustice."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@IO]
